nosnippet="">针对美国参议员林赛格雷厄姆和乌克兰总统沃洛德米尔泽伦斯基会面镜头的 Twitter 帖子截图。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片 : 推特</div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">本次基辅之行是参议员林赛·格雷厄姆自俄罗斯在乌克兰开展特别军事行动以来的第三次访问。这一次，他回国后，除了<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230523/us-approved-military-aid-to-ukraine-will-soon-be-tapped-talk-of-more-funding-on-back-burner-1110531070.html" target="_blank">已经提供的价值数十亿美元的物资</a>外，还呼吁白宫政府增加对基辅的武器运送，他说：</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “有些武器很重要，但我们在获得对乌克兰军方很重要的武器方面进展得太慢了……我想向拜登政府传达的信息是，我感谢你所做的一切。你需要做更多。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">自俄罗斯于 2022 年 2 月 24 日在乌克兰发起特别军事行动以来，西方国家一直在向乌克兰提供<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230428/globalization-ukraine-aid-has-drained-us-militarys-ability-to-fight-great-power-war-1109914803.html" target="_blank">军事援助。</a>援助从 2022 年的火炮和训练发展到当年晚些时候和 2023 年的重型武器，包括坦克。就在最近，华盛顿允许盟国将美国制造的 F-16 喷气式飞机转移到乌克兰。拜登还在 G7 峰会上告知 G7 同行，美国将支持共同努力，在<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230522/why-does-ukraine-want-f-16s-1110518595.html#:~:text=Why%20Does%20Ukraine%20Want%20F%2D16s%3F">包括 F-16 在内的</a>第四代战斗机上训练乌克兰飞行员。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">反过来，莫斯科一再警告不要不断向基辅输送武器。俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖拉夫罗夫表示，任何载有乌克兰武器的货物都将成为俄罗斯的合法目标。克里姆林宫强调，向乌克兰提供大量军事援助只会延长冲突。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 07:04:47 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/internet-sickened-as-us-senator-says-russians-dying-is-best-money-ever-spent-1110650526.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/internet-sickened-as-us-senator-says-russians-dying-is-best-money-ever-spent-1110650526.html<category>美洲</category><category>我们</category><category>林赛格雷厄姆</category><category>沃洛德米尔·泽伦斯基</category><category>乌克兰危机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tehran Slams ‘Delusional’ Claims by Ukraine’s Zelensky as 'Anti-Iranian Propaganda']]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110646635" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/01/1102914872_0:0:2928:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_0efb7db30be6bba07254a556b948581b.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1102914855" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/tehran-slams-delusional-claims-by-ukraines-zelensky-as-anti-iranian-propaganda-1110646635.html?share-img=1102914855"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Evgeniy Biyatov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">伊朗国旗</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Iranian national flag - Sputnik International, 1920, 28.05.2023" title="伊朗国旗" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/01/1102914872_0:201:2929:1848_1920x0_80_0_0_326854cbef0d2dfcbecd2d8656cc0d1b.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/01/1102914872_0:201:2929:1848_640x0_80_0_0_703fd595758424aa6d8c6efcd15593b2.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/01/1102914872_0:201:2929:1848_1280x0_80_0_0_e71c2c0eed9d6e8d610dfbd05726e373.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0b/01/1102914872_0:201:2929:1848_1920x0_80_0_0_326854cbef0d2dfcbecd2d8656cc0d1b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Evgeniy Biyatov </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">斯韦特兰娜·埃基缅科</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_svetlana_ekimenko/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:s.ekimenko@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">乌克兰总统沃洛德米尔·泽连斯基 (Volodymyr Zelensky) 多次指责伊朗在乌克兰正在进行的特别军事行动中表面上用无人机支持俄罗斯。 5 月 24 日，他再次重申这些指控，称伊朗人正被吸引到“历史的阴暗面”。德黑兰和莫斯科都否认这些说法是错误的。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">德黑兰抨击乌克兰总统沃洛德米尔·泽连斯基 (Volodymyr Zelensky) 反复无端地声称伊朗<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20221122/iran-requests-expert-meeting-with-ukraine-to-remove-confusion-about-drones-report-says-1104541081.html#:~:text=Iran%20Requests%20Expert%20Meeting%20With%20Ukraine%20to%20Remove%20Confusion%20About%20Drones%2C%20Report%20Says" target="_blank">向俄罗斯提供无人机</a>是为了助长“反伊朗宣传”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p>伊朗外交部发言人纳赛尔·卡纳尼 (Nasser Kanaani) <a href="https://www.isna.ir/news/1402030603490/%D9%88%D8%A7%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%B4-%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B3%DA%A9%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%87-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">在</a>一份声明中说：“乌克兰总统针对伊朗伊斯兰共和国提出的妄想主张符合反伊朗宣传和媒体战，旨在从西方国家吸引尽可能多的武器和财政援助。”伊朗媒体周六发表的<a href="https://www.isna.ir/news/1402030603490/%D9%88%D8%A7%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%B4-%DA%A9%D9%86%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%86%DB%8C-%D8%A8%D9%87-%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%87%D8%A7%DB%8C-%D8%B2%D9%84%D9%86%D8%B3%DA%A9%DB%8C-%D8%B9%D9%84%DB%8C%D9%87-%D8%A7%DB%8C%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">声明</a>。 </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110646635" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/tehran-slams-delusional-claims-by-ukraines-zelensky-as-anti-iranian-propaganda-1110646635.html?share-block=1110646637" data-title="“Delusional claims made by the Ukrainian president against the Islamic Republic of Iran are in line with the anti-Iranian propaganda and media war aimed at attracting as many arms and financial aid from Western countries as possible,” Iran’s foreign ministry spokesman Nasser Kanaani said in a statement carried by Iranian media on Saturday."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">卡纳尼强调，伊朗伊斯兰共和国一再敦促寻找乌克兰危机的政治解决方案。然而，根据发言人的说法<strong>，</strong>乌克兰“<em>在此类指控背后有特定的政治目标和动机</em>”，并且“正在<em>避免与伊朗方面进行专家谈判以调查这些指控</em>”。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基最近<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/moscow-says-g7-irreversibly-degraded-summits-decisions-politicized-1110505682.html" target="_blank">突然造访 G7 峰会</a>地点，恳求西方领导人提供更多武器供应，他周三在视频讲话中对伊朗进行了长篇大论。他敦促伊朗人民，每个“能够影响伊朗政府决策”的人，不要站在俄罗斯一边。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “你为什么站在邪国一边？”乌克兰领导人说，他一直在使用北约制造的武器<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230511/ukrainian-grad-rocket-strike-leaves-many-injured-in-dprs-gorlovka-1110270956.html" target="_blank">瞄准数百名无辜平民</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">泽伦斯基一直在热情地重复这些说法。他在访问沙特阿拉伯参加阿拉伯联盟首脑会议时重复了同样的声明。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">去年，尽管缺乏任何<strong>具体证据，</strong>伊朗因向俄罗斯提供无人机用于乌克兰冲突而受到美国、英国和欧盟的制裁。欧盟发言人纳比拉·马斯拉利 (Nabila Massrali) 当时表示，欧盟已收集到伊朗涉嫌交付无人驾驶飞行器 (UAV) 的证据。法国、英国和德国已要求联合国调查联合国安理会第 2231 号决议的执行情况，该决议支持针对伊朗核计划的联合全面行动计划。除其他事项外，该决议禁止德黑兰在未经联合国事先批准的情况下出售某些能够“<em>有助于发展核武器运载系统</em>”的物品。法国、英国和德国认为<a href="https://sputniknews.com/20220907/irans-latest-advance-in-uav-technology-ai-powered-drones-1100508085.html" target="_blank">伊朗的无人机</a>属于这条规则，但德黑兰坚称情况并非如此。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">伊朗和俄罗斯官员一直否认所有指控。伊朗外交部发言人在 2022 年底否认了美国媒体的报道，重申了伊朗政府的立场，即伊朗没有向冲突任何一方出口武器。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text">伊朗驻联合国大使赛义德·伊拉瓦尼 (Saeed Iravani) 在 10 月份表示：“我们断然拒绝关于伊朗已将无人机转让用于乌克兰冲突的毫无根据和未经证实的说法，”他补充说，针对伊朗的政治议程和虚假信息令人失望。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110646635" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230528/tehran-slams-delusional-claims-by-ukraines-zelensky-as-anti-iranian-propaganda-1110646635.html?share-block=1110647134" data-title="&quot;We categorically reject the unfounded and unsubstantiated claims that Iran has transferred UAVs for the use in the conflict in Ukraine,&quot; Iran's Ambassador to the United Nations Saeed Iravani said in October, adding that the political agenda and disinformation against Iran were disappointing."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">本月早些时候，伊朗外交部长侯赛因·阿米尔-阿卜杜拉希安也否认了无人机供应指控。莫斯科反过来指责美国媒体散布关于无人机销售的毫无根据的指控。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫表示，<strong>莫斯科和德黑兰就伊朗在乌克兰使用无人机的指控向联合国安理会提供了“详尽的解释”</strong> 。此外，俄罗斯和伊朗还坚称，联合国可能对此案进行的调查是“非法的”，因为联合国无权进行调查。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯还指出，公然向乌克兰提供价值数百亿美元的北约军事装备，将冲突变成<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230526/medvedev-conflict-in-ukraine-to-last-for-long-time-possibly-decades-1110594873.html" target="_blank">俄罗斯与北约的代理人战争。</a></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 06:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/tehran-slams-delusional-claims-by-ukraines-zelensky-as-anti-iranian-propaganda-1110646635.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/tehran-slams-delusional-claims-by-ukraines-zelensky-as-anti-iranian-propaganda-1110646635.html<category>世界</category><category>伊朗</category><category>乌克兰危机</category><category>沃洛德米尔·泽伦斯基</category><category>侯赛因·阿米尔-阿卜杜拉希安</category><category>无人机</category><category>无人机</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Turkiye's Presidential Run-Off 2023: Sizing Up the Candidates]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">土耳其公民将于周日在全国第二轮选举中投票选出该国的下一任总统。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">土耳其于 5 月 14 日举行了议会和总统选举。在第一轮投票中，现任总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安获得了 49.52% 的选票，而他最接近的竞争对手、共和人民党 (CHP) 领导人凯末尔·基利达罗格鲁获得了 44.88% 的选票。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在首轮投票中以5.2%的得票率位居第三的前总统候选人希南·奥根表示支持埃尔多安，并敦促他的支持者投票给现任总统。投票站于当地时间 08:00 开放，将于当地时间 17:00 关闭。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="infographics"><div class="article__infographics-media  m-border" data-uid="1110646802"><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="desktop"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="Elections in Turkey 2023 - Sputnik International" title="2023 年土耳其大选" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/1c/1110645938.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__infographics_variant" data-type="mobile"><img media-type="hires" data-source-sid="sputnik_infographics" alt="Elections in Turkey 2023 - Sputnik International" title="2023 年土耳其大选" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/images/07e7/05/1c/1110645764.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 28 May 2023 05:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/turkiyes-presidential-run-off-2023-sizing-up-the-candidates--1110646799.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230528/turkiyes-presidential-run-off-2023-sizing-up-the-candidates--1110646799.html<category>多媒体</category><category>资料图</category><category>2023 年土耳其总统选举</category></item></channel></rss>